<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Coffee House</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f2ee;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541167715-f5e2747d969f?q=80&w=2670&auto=format&fit=crop') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 100vh;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        nav ul a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .hero {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #795548;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #5d4037;
        }

        main {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #795548;
        }

        #about p {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .menu-items {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .menu-item {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1 1 200px;
        }

        .menu-item h3 {
            color: #5d4037;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        #contact {
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">BiNS Daily Dose</div>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#menu">Menu</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Your Daily Dose of Delight</h1>
            <p>Experience the perfect blend of tradition and taste.</p>
            <a href="#menu" class="cta-button">Explore Our Menu</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="about">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded on a passion for quality and community, The Coffee House is more than just a place to get coffee. We source the finest beans from around the world to bring you a truly exceptional experience. Every cup is crafted with care, because we believe great coffee brings people together.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="menu">
            <h2>Our Menu</h2>
            <div class="menu-items">
                <div class="menu-item">
                    <h3>Espresso</h3>
                    <p>A rich, concentrated shot of coffee.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="menu-item">
                    <h3>Latte</h3>
                    <p>Espresso with steamed milk and a light layer of foam.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="menu-item">
                    <h3>Cappuccino</h3>
                    <p>Equal parts espresso, steamed milk, and milk foam.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="menu-item">
                    <h3>Cold Brew</h3>
                    <p>Slow-steeped coffee for a smooth, less acidic taste.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Visit Us</h2>
            <p>Poblacion, San Jose, Negros Oriental</p>
            <p>Phone: 09055999154</p>
            <p>Email: binsdailydose@gmail.come</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 The Coffee House. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>